---
// ReconciliationTerminal.astro - Self-healing cluster monitoring terminal
---

<div
  class="bg-[#0d1117] rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-4 font-mono text-xs md:text-sm shadow-2xl"
>
  <!-- Fake Terminal Header -->
  <div class="flex gap-2 mb-4 border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">
    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
    <span class="ml-2 text-gray-500">zsh â€” pypctl watch</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="space-y-1">
    <div class="flex gap-2">
      <span class="text-[#00D9A3] font-bold">$</span>
      <span class="text-white">pypctl watch --reconciliation-loop</span>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-3 space-y-1">
      <div class="text-gray-400">
        <span class="text-blue-400">[INFO]</span> Checking state for cluster: CORE-01
      </div>
      <div class="text-green-400">
        <span class="text-green-500">[OK]</span> Control Plane latency &lt; 12ms
      </div>
      <div class="text-green-400">
        <span class="text-green-500">[OK]</span> BGP Peering established (ASN 64500)
      </div>
      <div class="text-yellow-400">
        <span class="text-yellow-500">[WARN]</span> Node-03: Memory pressure detected
        (&gt;85%)
      </div>
      <div class="text-purple-400">
        <span class="text-purple-500">[AUTO]</span> Triggering pod eviction policy...
      </div>
      <div class="text-blue-400">
        <span class="text-blue-400">[INFO]</span> Moving workload "database-shard-2"
        to Node-01
      </div>
      <div class="text-green-400">
        <span class="text-green-500">[OK]</span> Rescheduling complete. Zero downtime
        observed.
      </div>
      <div class="text-blue-400">
        <span class="text-blue-400">[INFO]</span> Snapshotting state to S3... Done.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-3 text-gray-500 border-t border-gray-800 mt-3 pt-2">
      # System is self-healing. Human intervention not required.
    </div>

    <div class="text-gray-500 animate-pulse mt-2">
      <span class="inline-block">_</span> Waiting for events...
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
